Description-Content-Type: text/markdown

# QT build utils


## Development
```sh
uv sync --all-extras --dev
```

## Usage
Edit ui in designer

```sh
qt-build-utils edit [ui_file]
```

Convert ui to py

```sh
qt-build-utils convert [ui_file] -i
```
